quran[123]{c,v,t}:
  11,1,"AlĂŽ. Tazmamt, issekniyen iS ppuĂ»ewwben, sinna, ppufeĂ»Ă»len s$uĂŽ UĂ»wib i IpwaxebbĂŽen"
  11,2,"Ur Ăąabdet siwa Ăebbi. Nek, s$uĂŽeS $uĂŽwen, d aneddaĂŽ u d abcir"
  11,3,"Ssutret ssmaĂȘ i Mass nnwen, steĂŽoĂąet aS, ad IfeĂŽĂŽeo fellawen afeĂŽĂŽeo ilhan, ar lajel ipwassnen. Ippak lfevl iS i yal bab n lfevl. Ma twexxĂŽem, nekk ugade$ a ppeppuĂąqbem, ass ameqwran"
  11,4,"Tu$alin nnwen, ar Ăebbi. Neppa Izmer i yal cci"
  11,5,"Day nitni, s tidep, ur snefvasen ara idmaren nnsen, iwakken ad ffren fellaS? Xas $ummen s iceĂźĂźiven nnsen, day ur IĂ©ĂŽa ara ayen teffren akked wayen d qqaĂŽen? Neppa, s tidep, Issen i illan deg idmaren"
  11,6,"Ur illi lweĂȘc di tmurt, mebla ma illa ĂŽĂŽeĂ©q is ar Ăebbi. Issen tanezdu$t is, tanĂźelt is. MeĂŽĂŽa, di Tezmamt ipbegginen"
  11,7,"D Neppa i Ixelqen tamurt akked igenwan di sdis wussan. Asgeld iS illa $ef waman. A kwen IjeĂŽĂŽeb anwi segwen ara ixedmen ayen ilhan, sennig wiyav. Ma tenniv: \"ih, kunwi a d tekkrem deffir tmeppant nnwen\", wid ijehlen, war ccekk, a d inin: \"ayagi, kan, d ssĂȘur n Ă»Ă»eĂȘ"
  11,8,"Ma NeswexxeĂŽ asen aĂąaqeb ar imir ipwassnen, war ccekk, a d inin: \"d acu iT iĂźĂźfen\"? Ass ideg ara ten id iawev, day illa wa ara ten iveĂŽĂŽfen segs? Ad asen izzi wayen i$ef pmmaĂąliken"
  11,9,"Ma NesĂȘess i umdan aĂȘunu nneÂšÂŁ, sinna, Nekkes as t, atan ad iayes, ad ijhel"
  11,10,"Ma NesĂȘess as l$it, deffir twa$it i t innulen, atan ad yini: \"fukkent felli lemĂȘayen\", d$a, neppa, ad ifĂŽeĂȘ, ad izux"
  11,11,"Kkes ed wid iĂ»ebbĂŽen, ixeddmen ayen ilhan. I widak ssmaĂȘ akked tikci meqqwĂŽen"
  11,12,"Ahat teppaoav kra n wayen ik ed ippuweĂȘĂȘan. Pzemmiven yis idmaren ik mara qqaĂŽen: \"a lemmer i s d irs ugerruj, ne$ idda d, yides, lmelk\"! KeĂ§Ă§ d aneddaĂŽ kan. Ăebbi d Awkil n yal cci"
  11,13,"Ne$ ad inin: \"isnulfa t id\". Ini: \"awit ed, s usnulfu, mraw n tsuĂŽtin am neppa. NaĂąĂŽet ayen iwumi tzemrem, war Ăebbi, ma tessawalem tidep"
  11,14,"Ma ur awen d rran ara, cfut ar irs ed kan s tussna n Ăebbi, ar ur illi ĂŽebbi siwa Neppa. Ihi, ma kunwi d imvuĂąen"
  11,15,"I wid ib$an tameddurt n ddunit akked ĂŽĂŽĂȘuĂȘ is, a Nkafi, degs, igiten nnsen, ur asen Ntekkes"
  11,16,"Widak, ur ppafen, di laxeĂŽt, siwa times. Ad i$li wayen Ă»enĂąen degs; inqev wayen xeddmen"
  11,17,"Day win iddan d ubeggen, s$uĂŽ Mass is, u immal as t unagi s$uĂŽeSâŠ? U, uqbel is, Tazmamt n Musa, d nnhaya u d aĂȘunu. Wigi umnen yis. Win i p inekĂŽen, seg ikubar, ppaĂąud is d times. Ur ppili di ccekk fellas. Neppa, ih, d tidep s$uĂŽ Mass ik. Maca, tegwti n medden ur ppamnen"
  11,18,"Anwa idensen sennig win id isnulfan tikerkas $ef Ăebbi? Wigi a d rsen i Mass nnsen. A d inin inagan: \"d wigi i iskaddben $ef Mass nnsen\". Day Ăebbi ur Ixezzu yara imednas"
  11,19,"I isĂźixxiĂŽen seg ubrid n Ăebbi, i t issarmen d uĂąwij, nitni ur uminen s laxeĂŽt"
  11,20,"Wigi, ur sfunnugen di tmurt, ur asen illi bab, war Ăebbi. Fellasen aĂąaqeb ar wayev. Ur zmiren ad slen, ur pwalin"
  11,21,D wigi i isxesĂŽen iman nnsen. Itelf iten wayen d snulfuyen
  11,22,"Ur illi ccekk, ih, nitni ad xesĂŽen, di laxeĂŽt, sennig wiyav"
  11,23,"Ih, wid iumnen, u xeddmen ayen ilhan, u unzen aS i Mass nnsen, widak d at Loennet, degs ad wekkĂŽen"
  11,24,"Amedya n snat n trebbuyaĂą am uder$al, uĂąĂ©Ă©ug, akked win ipwalin, win isellen. Day Ăąadlen sin imedyaten agi? Day ur d tesmektayem ara"
  11,25,"Ni$ Nuzen ed NuĂȘ i ugdud is: \"nek d aneddaĂŽ nnwen ipbegginen"
  11,26,"iwakken ur tĂąabdem siwa Ăebbi. Nek ugaded aĂąaqeb fellawen, ass aqeĂŽhan"
  11,27,"Nnan imvebbĂŽen, wid ijehlen, seg ugdud is: \"keĂ§Ă§, $uĂŽne$, d amdan am nekwni. Nwala, d ĂŽĂŽdiyen nne$, kan, war ameyyez, i k ivefĂŽen. Ur nwala s wacu i $ tifem. XaĂźi, nĂȘesb ikwen d ikeddaben"
  11,28,"Inna: \"a yagdud iw! Acu twalam ma ddi$ d ubeggen n Mass iw? Ifka yi d aĂȘunu s$uĂŽeS. Idreg fellawen. Day a t nĂȘeppem fellawen, ma kunwi tugim t"
  11,29,"A yagdud iw! Ur awen ssuture$ ayla, ilmend is; taqdiĂąt iw ar Ăebbi kan. Ur ppara$, nek, wid iumnen. S tidep, ad mlilen d Mass nnsen. Maca, nek wala$ kwen d agdud ur nessin"
  11,30,"A yagdud iw! Acu ara yi isellken seg ufus n Ăebbi, lemmer i ten rri$ akin, day ur d tesmektayem ara"
  11,31,"Ur awen qqaĂŽe$: $uĂŽi lexzayen n Ăebbi. Ur ssine$ tabavnit. Ur qqaĂŽe$: nek d lmelk. Ur qqaĂŽe$ i wid ĂȘeqĂŽent wallen nnwen: ur asen Ippak ara Ăebbi lxiĂŽ, d awez$i. Yif akw Ăebbi akken IĂ©ĂŽa, i illan deg iman nnsen. Mulac ad ili$ seg imednas"
  11,32,"Nnan: \"a NuĂȘ! Ni$ tnamrev a$, tessugtev a$ anamer. Ihi, awi ya$ d ayen i $ tĂąahdev, ma tessawalev tidep"
  11,33,"Inna: \"d Ăebbi kan ar awen t id Iawin, ma ihwa yaS. Kunwi ur tesfunnugem"
  11,34,"Xas b$i$ a kwen neĂ»ĂȘe$, ur tesfaydayam seg wanĂ»aĂȘ iw, ma Ib$a Ăebbi a kwen Itlef. Neppa d Mass nnwen; tu$alin nnwen $uĂŽeS"
  11,35,"Ne$ qqaĂŽen: \"isnulfa t id\". Ini: \"ma snulfa$ t id, lbe$wv iw i yiri w. Nek, ur ppka$ di lbe$wv nnwen"
  11,36,"IppuweĂȘĂȘa d i NuĂȘ: \"ur ippamen yiwen, d awez$i, seg ugdud ik, siwa wid illan umnen. Ihi, ur k icqi wayen xeddmen"
  11,37,"EĂ»naĂą lbabuĂŽ, ger wallen nneÂŁ, s uweĂȘĂȘi nneÂŁ. Ur iyI d pmeslay $ef wid idensen, war ccekk, ad $emqen"
  11,38,"La iĂ»ennaĂą lbabuĂŽ. Yal tikelt ara Ăąaddin $uĂŽes imvebbĂŽen n ugdud is, tkaĂąriren fellas. Inna: \"ma temmaĂąlkem degne$, ihi, a nemmaĂąlek degwen akken temmaĂąlkem"
  11,39,"Deqqal a ppeĂ©ĂŽem, u$uĂŽ ara d ias uĂąaqeb ara t isdullen, ara iĂȘaz uĂąaqeb imezgi"
  11,40,"Alamma, mi d iusa lameĂŽ nneÂŁ, la pfeggiven igwefran d ihedman, Nenna: \"awi degs tayuga n yal Ă»Ă»enf, tawacult ik - siwa wid i$ef id izwar wawal -, akked wid iumnen\". Drus kan i iumnen yides"
  11,41,"Inna: \"rekbet degs, s yisem n Ăebbi, acali s akked trusi s. Mass iw, s tidep, IpsemmiĂȘ, IpĂȘunu"
  11,42,"Icula yissen, di lemwao anect idurar. Issawel NuĂȘ i mmi s, i illan weĂȘdes: \"a mmi ali d yidne$, ur teppiliv ar ijehliyen"
  11,43,"Inna: \"Ă»Ă»ĂŽan iw d adrar, ad iyi isellek seg waman\". Inna: \"assa, ulac leslak si lameĂŽ n Ăebbi, siwa i win i$ef IĂȘun\". Ăaddant lemwao garasen. IĂ»ebĂȘ ed seg wid ipwa$emqen"
  11,44,"Nnan: \"a tamurt, seblaĂą aman im, a yigenni eĂ»Ă»fu\". Aman zzren. IĂ»aĂŽ lameĂŽ: irs $ef Loudi. Iffe$ uberraĂȘ: akin agdud imednas"
  11,45,"Inuj NuĂȘ ar Mass is, inna: \"a Mass iw! Ni$ mmi n twacult iw. Ih, lemĂąahda K d tidep, KeĂ§Ă§ Tifev akw imĂȘaddan"
  11,46,"Inna: \"a NuĂȘ! Neppa, s tidep, ur illi n wacult ik. Ih, neppa ur ixdim ayen ilhan. Ihi, ur iyI d steqsay $ef wayen ur tessinev. Nek a k Ssakwaye$, ur teppiliv seg wid ur nessin"
  11,47,"Inna: \"a Mass iw! Ili di lĂąawen iw, iwakken ur K id steqsaye$ $ef wayen ur ssine$. Ma ur iyi TsemmĂȘev, ur TĂȘunev felli, ad ili$ seg imexsuĂŽen"
  11,48,"Nnan d: \"a NuĂȘ! Ers ed s tifrat s$uĂŽneÂŁ, akked lbaĂŽaka, fellak akw $ef leoyus i illan yidek. Kra n legyus, a ten N$it. Sinna, fellasen s$uĂŽneÂŁ, aĂąaqeb aqeĂŽĂȘan"
  11,49,"Tagi si teqĂ»ivin n tbavnit, NweĂȘĂȘa yak tent. Ur tent tessinev, keĂ§Ă§, ne$ agdud ik, uqbel wagi. Ihi, eĂ»beĂŽ, taggara, war ccekk, i wid ipĂȘezziben"
  11,50,"I Ăad, gmat sen Hud, inna: \"a yagdud iw! Ăabdet Ăebbi! Ur tesĂąim ĂŽebbi, war Neppa. Kunwi tesnulfuyem d kan"
  11,51,"A yagdud iw! Ur awen ssuture$ taqdiĂąt $ef waya. TaqdiĂąt iw ar Win kan, iyi d Ixelqen. Day ur tefhimem ara"
  11,52,"A yagdud iw! Ssutret ssmaĂȘ i Mass nnwen, sinna, steĂŽoĂąet aS. Ad awen d Isse$li ageffur d ihedman, ad awen irnu tazmert i tezmert nnwen. Ur ppu$alet d ibe$wviyen"
  11,53,"Nnan as: \"a Hud! Ur a$ d tusid s ubeggen, ur neppaoa, nekwni, iĂŽebbiten nne$, ilmend n wawal ik, ur numin yisek"
  11,54,"NeqqaĂŽ kan, d kra iĂŽebbiten nne$, i k i$eĂŽqen\". Inna: \"nek, Anagi w d Ăebbi, u cehhdet ar ur ppka$ ara deg wayen tepcarakem"
  11,55,"war Neppa. Ihi, andit iyi akken ma tellam, sinna ur iyi sganayet"
  11,56,"Nek, ppekle$ af Ăebbi, Mass iw u Mass nnwen. Ur illi umexluq ur IĂźĂźif seg ixef is. Ih, Mass iw deg ubrid uwqim"
  11,57,"Ma wexxĂŽen, ni$ ssawve$ awen d ayen i$ef id ppuceggĂąa$ $uĂŽwen. A d InĂ»ef, Mass iw, agdud war kunwi. Ur T teĂźĂźuĂŽum s wacemma. Mass iw, s tidep, d AmĂȘareb n yal cci"
  11,58,"Mi d iusa lameĂŽ nneÂŁ, Nsellek Hud akked wid iumnen yides, s uĂȘunu s$uĂŽneÂŁ. Nsellek iten seg uĂąaqeb uwĂąiĂŽ"
  11,59,"Akka Ăad. NekĂŽen issekniyen n Mass nnsen, ĂąuĂ»an imazanen iS. Ddan d lameĂŽ n yal aqehhaĂŽ iggernennen"
  11,60,"A ten ivfeĂŽ xezzu di ddunit agi, u deg wass n tnekra. Day, war ccekk, ur jhilen ara Ăad, ar Mass nnsen? Day maĂ§Ă§i: \"akin Ăad, agdud n Hud"
  11,61,"I Tamud, gmat sen ĂĂŒĂaliĂȘ, inna: \"a yagdud iw! Ăabdet Ăebbi! Ur tesĂąim ĂŽebbi, war Neppa. Neppa Ixelq ikwen seg wakal, Izzde$ ikwen fellas. Ssutret aS ssmaĂȘ, sinna, steĂŽoĂąet aS. Mass iw, s tidep, IqeĂŽb ed, Ippara d awal"
  11,62,"Nnan as: \"a ĂaliĂȘ, ni$ telliv garane$, uqbel aya, d asirem nne$. Day ad a$ tekksev aĂąbad n wayen Ăąabden imezwura nne$? Nekwni, s tidep, aql a$ di ccekk imcebbwel, $ef wayen u$uĂŽ la $ tneccdev"
  11,63,"Inna: \"a yagdud iw! Acu twalam ma ddi$ d ubeggen n Mass iw? Ifka yi d aĂȘunu s$uĂŽeS. Acu ara yi isellken seg ufus n Ăebbi, ma aĂąĂ»a$ $uĂŽeS? Iyi ternam, siwa taxessaĂŽt"
  11,64,"A yagdud iw! Tagi d tal$wemt n Ăebbi, d assekni i kunwi. Eooet ep a ppeks di tmurt n Ăebbi. Ur p pjeyyifet, mulac a kwen id isami uĂąaqeb iqeĂŽben"
  11,65,"Gezmen as ivaĂŽen. Inna: \"zhut deg ixxamen nnwen, krav wussan. Apan lemĂąahda ur nepwankaĂŽ"
  11,66,"Mi d iusa lameĂŽ nneÂŁ, Nsellek ĂaliĂȘ akked wid iumnen yides, s uĂȘunu s$uĂŽneÂŁ, si ddell n wass nni. Ih, Mass ik d Uohid, d Uzmir"
  11,67,"Asu$u iwwet wid idensen, gwran d d imeslax deg ixxamen nnsen"
  11,68,"amzun ur rbiĂȘen degsen. Day, s tidep, ur jhilen ara Tamud, ar Mass nnsen? Day maĂ§Ă§i: \"akin Tamud"
  11,69,"Ni$ usan d imceggĂąen nneÂŁ ar IbĂŽahim, s ubecceĂŽ. Nnan: \"tifrat\"! Inna: \"tifrat\"! Ur iĂąaĂźĂźel ara ibbwi d aĂąjmi icwin"
  11,70,"Mi iwala ifassen nnsen ur d Ă©Ă©ilen ara $uĂŽes, isĂȘassef iten, iugad iten. Nnan: \"ur ppagwad, nekwni neppuceggaĂą ed ar ugdud n LuĂź"
  11,71,"TameĂźĂźut is tbedd, tevĂ»a. NbecceĂŽ ip s IsĂȘaq, akked YaĂąqub, deffir IsĂȘaq"
  11,72,"Tenna: \"a lĂȘif iw, day a d arwe$, nek d tam$aĂŽt, u argaz agi inu, wesser? Ayagi, s tidep, d lwehma"
  11,73,"Nnan: \"day twehmev di lameĂŽ n Ăebbi? AĂȘunu n Ăebbi, akked lbaĂŽaka S, fellawen ay at uxxam. Ih, Neppa d AmaĂązuz, MucaĂą"
  11,74,"Mi s tekkes tugwdi i IbĂŽahim, u iusa t id ubecceĂŽ, inumer aÂŁ $ef ugdud n LuĂź"
  11,75,"IbĂŽahim, s tidep, iĂȘellem, ippanez, isteĂŽoiĂą"
  11,76,"A IbĂŽahim, ur keĂ§Ă§em deg waya. Ni$ iusa d lameĂŽ n Mass ik. Nitni, a ten id ias uĂąaqeb, war tifrat"
  11,77,"Mi usan imceggĂąen nneÂŁ ar LuĂź, innu$ben, ur isĂąi i$il a ten ifukk. Inna: \"wagi d ass uwĂąiĂŽ"
  11,78,"Iusa d ugdud is, zeĂȘfen d $uĂŽes. Llan, zik, xeddmen tucmitin. Inna: \"a yagdud iw! Atent an issi, nitenti zeddigit, i kunwi. Ăezbet i Ăebbi, ur iyi pĂȘeccimet ar inebgawen iw. Day ur illi ara, garawen, urgaz aĂȘesbi"
  11,79,"Nnan: \"ni$ teĂ©ĂŽiv ur nesĂąi lĂȘeqq deg issi k. KeĂ§Ă§, s tidep, teĂ©ĂŽiv d acu neb$a"
  11,80,"Inna: \"a lemmer i wen zmire$, ne$ sĂąi$ tayep ioehden"
  11,81,"Nnan: \"a LuĂź, nekwni d imceggĂąen n Mass ik. Ur k id ppawven. ĂuĂȘ akked twacult ik, deg iv. Yiwen degwen ur d itezzi! Kkes ed tameĂźĂźut ik. Neppat, s tidep, a ppepwwet s wayen ara ten iwwten. Ih, ppaĂąud nnsen, taĂ»ebĂȘit. Ni$ tqeĂŽb ed tĂ»ebĂȘit"
  11,82,"Mi d iusa lameĂŽ nneÂŁ, Nesredm ip. Nesse$li d fellas abruri n yiĂ©ĂŽa ibelbaven n talaxt"
  11,83,"Pwanesxen ar Mass ik. Nitni, ur bĂąiden i imednas"
  11,84,"I Madian, gmat sen CuĂąayeb, inna: \"a yagdud iw! Ăabdet Ăebbi! Ur tesĂąim ĂŽebbi, war Neppa. Ur ssenqaset di lkil akked lmizan. Nek, wala$ kwen teĂŽwam, u ugade$ fellawen aĂąaqeb, ass itezzin"
  11,85,"A yagdud iw! Ktilet, weznet, s lewqama. Ur ĂźĂźuĂŽĂŽut imdanen deg wayla nnsen, ur pdenniset, tessefsadem di tmurt"
  11,86,"Yif it i kunwi wayen d iqqimen i Ăebbi, ma d lmumnin ay tellam. Ur lli$, nek, d amĂȘareb nnwen"
  11,87,"Nnan: \"a CuĂąayeb, day a$ umĂŽen wawalen ik, a neoo ayen Ăąabden imezwura nne$? Ne$ a nexdem, deg wayla nne$, ayen ur a$ nehwi? KeĂ§Ă§, s tidep, d uĂȘlim, d uĂ»wib"
  11,88,"Inna: \"a yagdud iw! Acu twalam, ma ddi$ d ubeggen n Mass iw? I$at iyi yis, l$it imaĂąnen. Ur b$i$ a kwen mgirrde$, siwa $ef wayen i wen gedle$. B$i$ kan, s wayen zemre$, ad awen Ă»egme$ tikli. LĂąawen iw s$uĂŽ Ăebbi kan. Ppekle$ fellaS, utube$ T"
  11,89,"A yagdud iw! Awer kwen teppara nnmara w d ibe$wviyen, a ppevĂŽu yidwen akken tevĂŽa d ugdud n NuĂȘ, ne$ win n Hud, ne$ win n ĂaliĂȘ! Agdud n LuĂź, ur ibĂąad ara segwen"
  11,90,"Ssutret ssmaĂȘ i Mass nnwen, sinna, steroĂąet aS. Mass iw, s tidep, IpĂȘunu, IpĂȘemmil"
  11,91,"Nnan: \"a CuĂąayeb, ur nefhim ara aĂźas n wayen id tenniv. Aql a$ nwala k d uĂŽhif garane$. Lemmer maĂ§Ă§i d alag ik, war ccekk, a k neĂŽoem. Ur a$ tezmirev"
  11,92,"Inna: \"a yagdud iw! Day Ăebbi, $uĂŽwen, yif iT walag iw, di tezmert? Terram T ar deffir n waĂąrur nnwen. Mass iw, s tidep, Izzi i wayen txeddmem"
  11,93,"A yagdud iw! Xedmet deg umekkan nnwen, nek ad xedme$. Deqqal a ppeĂ©ĂŽem, u$uĂŽ ara d ias uĂąaqeb ara t isdullen, anwa ay d akeddab. Ăasset, nek, yidwen, ad Ăąasse"
  11,94,"Mi d iusa lameĂŽ nneÂŁ, Nsellek CuĂąayeb akked wid iumnen yides, s uĂȘunu s$uĂŽneÂŁ. Asu$u iwwet wid idensen, gwran d d imeslax deg ixxamen nnsen"
  11,95,"amzun ur rbiĂȘen degsen. Day maĂ§Ă§i: \"akin Madian\"! Am: \"akin Tamud"
  11,96,"Ni$ Nuzen ed Musa, s issekniyen nneÂŁ, akked udabu n Ă»Ă»eĂȘ"
  11,97,uĂŽ FerĂąun akked imvebbĂŽen is. Ddan d lameĂŽ n FerĂąun. LameĂŽ n FerĂąun ur illi d uĂ»wib
  11,98,"Ad izwir i ugdud is, ass n tnekra, a ten inheĂŽ ar usario n tmes. A yasario ucmit u$uĂŽ pwanehĂŽen"
  11,99,"A ten ivfeĂŽ xezzu di tagi, u deg wass n tnekra. A tikci tucmip ippunefken"
  11,100,"Ayagi, si teqĂ»ivin n temdinin, i k d Nessawal. Garasent tid ibedden, tid ipwamegren"
  11,101,"Ur ten Nednis. Maca, densen iman nnsen. Ur ten nefĂąan s wacemma, iĂŽebbiten nnsen i la naĂąĂŽen, war Ăebbi, mi d iusa lameĂŽ n Mass ik. I sen rnan, siwa ssxev"
  11,102,"Akka tiyta n Mass ik. Mi Iwwet timdinin i idensen, s tidep, tiyta S teqĂŽeĂȘ, teqseĂȘ"
  11,103,"Ih, deg waya, assekni i wid iugaden aĂąaqeb n laxeĂŽt. Ass nni, d ass unejmaĂą n yimdanen. Ass nni, d ass n ccada"
